sentences.sentence: The country now measures 160.475 sq KMS. Two-thirds of that are mountains.
sentences.translation: 测量后，其国境线总长度为77.9公里，国土面积达到160.475平方公里，其中三分之二为山地。

sentences.sentence: Inconveniently, the Inambari dam would flood 120 KMS of the highway, on which upgrading work has already begun.
sentences.translation: 令人不解的是，Inambari大坝将淹没这条公路其中一段120公里，高架工程已经开始进行。

sentences.sentence: An interesting cosmetic change to the kernel boot process and graphics mode is called the kernel-based mode setting (KMS).
sentences.translation: 对内核引导过程和图像模式的一个有趣更改是基于内核的模式设置(KMS)。
